      "content": "it’s just that \"making a change\" sounds like so much work. like i have to fight every single day just to exist, and i'm just so done fighting. sometimes i think the only way to actually stop the cycle is to just... stop altogether. like, if there's no more feeling, then there's no more pain. doesn't that make sense?",
